data.description: This corner lot in Harpers Preserve is a must-see! The two-story home features an open floor plan, wood-like vinyl floors, and high ceilings with blinds. The kitchen, which includes a large island, flows into the family room, making it a great space for entertaining. The backyard is spacious and includes an extended covered patio perfect for gatherings. With four bedrooms, three bathrooms, a study, and a family room, this home is ideal for families. Don't let this dream home slip away!
